Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:55.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,320)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很清楚自己今天要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know exactly what I'm gonna eat today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  话说我干啥要进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, why did I come in here, again?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lemme guess--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.17,0:01:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹字开头的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Starts with a K
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把肉饼放烤架上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Throwin' patties on the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.86,0:01:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿着配料玩杂耍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Juggling ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万不要撒一地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trying not to spill
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架点上火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The grill aflame
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作似玩乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work is a game
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大功告成  就能拥有面包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I'm done, you'll have a bun
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充满无限美味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Full of yum, yum, yum
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的计划完美实现中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My plan is working perfectly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三度烫伤不算
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Minus the third degree burns
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在巧妙撤出蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, for my clever escape
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想趁外卖还没送出去偷偷溜走是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trying to sneak out before the big delivery, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没必要临阵脱逃  小小蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No need to get cold feet, little patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.85,0:02:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在新家一定会幸福快乐不少的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be very happy in your new home
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我送外卖要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be late for my delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}八十分钟后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,420)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  小小蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, little patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就快到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're almost home
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:48.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1028,820)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:48.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1444,470)}泥巴海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:48.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,866)}百慕大三角
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有软软的东西给我做缓冲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something soft broke my fall
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.15,0:03:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们好像已经出裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think we're in Bikini Bottom anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们肯定是在泥巴海迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must be lost in the deep Goo Sea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来外卖送不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll miss the delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让可怜的蟹老板失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've let down poor, old Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to the, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上个小号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,little patty's room?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会小心转过身去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll discreetly turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你点隐私的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give you a little privacy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没做过小号蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't make little patties
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想得美  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  我们被困了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, we're marooned
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须把蟹黄堡留到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to make this patty last
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我们获救前的唯一食物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's our only food until we're rescued
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.16,0:03:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想表达什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是想活下来  就必须分享
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna survive, we'll have to share
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分享
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Share?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一言为定  大兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got yourself a deal, big boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来握个手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put 'er there, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  你可以吃第一口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have the first bite
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃得少一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it a small one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不介意我就开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's strange
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这蟹黄堡味道有点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This patty tastes a little
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,angry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.24,0:04:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're okay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为要失去你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I lost you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须趁还没天黑赶紧开始找避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to start looking for shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before it gets dark
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那蛇怪先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about Mr. Snake Monster?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟我们一块避难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can he come stay with us?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.08,0:05:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不算太破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not too shabby
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  能把腿挪过去一点点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, could you move your leg over a little?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有点挤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a bit cramped in here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好有刺可以做缓冲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky these thorns broke our fall
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  我真是幸好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, lucky me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方看着挺宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place looks pretty spacious
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全可以在这整不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can really do a lot with this place
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边可以当你房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over there can be your room
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边可以当我房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That could be my room
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里头是不是有点黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a little dark back here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以听到我回声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can hear my echo
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.91,0:05:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有没有觉得里面有点湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does it feel a little wet in here to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到电灯开关了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found a light switch
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,New plan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's grab a bite to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bananas
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算有东西吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, some grub
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's eat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要吃这块石头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should we eat this rock?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll eat anything
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave us alone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,836)}开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(566,440)}椰子小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1216,344)}盛大开业
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天的活儿干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great work out there today
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有你的生活完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just not the same without you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有你的生活完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just not the same without you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想的跟我一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you thinkin' what I'm thinkin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我也拿不定主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, I can't decide either
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,员工运动衫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do the company sports jerseys
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要米黄色还是绿色才好看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look better in beige or green?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you imbecile
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在得逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to am-scray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不知物不觉地回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get back home without the monsters noticing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物到处都在盯着我们  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're watching us everywhere, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻潜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nose dive
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太多怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too many monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1092,252)}椰子小屋
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.55,0:08:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow my lead
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了怪物们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, monsters
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这就回去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll go back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上去做好吃的椰子堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and whip up some nice coconut patties
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.85,0:09:10.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们为大家准备了盛大又美味的惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:10.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we have a big, delicious surprise for you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你们闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just have to close your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把耳朵捂住  然后唱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now stick your fingers in your ears and sing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁现在快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, run
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:27.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1340,380)}正在供应\N椰子堡
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.73,0:09:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,威胁吃掉我们  俘虏我们的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,friends who kept us captive by threatening to eat us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你办法想得可真好  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great thinking back there, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来庆祝一下胜利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about we celebrate our victory?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.36,0:09:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们怎么朝岛那边往回走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are we heading back to the island?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得是岛在朝我们这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think the island is heading back to us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,868)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Comin' through
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚才真是好险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(570,438)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你迟到了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're late, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你前六年都哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where have you been the last six years?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光就这么结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it was nice while it lasted
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1374,286)}无海绵宝宝\N天数
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地震来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an earthquake
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吃蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not me restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:18.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(764,384)}正在供应\N椰子堡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道我今天想吃什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what I want to eat today
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份椰子堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have one coco patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Comin' right up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过要收点小小的服务费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a nominal service charge
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在皆大欢喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eh, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们总算一块儿独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're alone at last
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.64,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs160}派大星\N{\fs50} \N{\fs160}快点骑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(704,368)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:50.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(658,620)}分镜指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(746,532)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(582,538)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来骑自行车穿越水母田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna go for a bike ride through jellyfish fields?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bet your square pants I do
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱骑车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love bike riding
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了我没自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot I don't have a bike
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有辆备用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a spare
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先等一下  我找车得找好一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, it'll just take me a minute to find it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像找不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't seem to
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Find it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这辆上品好车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check out this sweet ride
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Gare Bear
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to ride a bike
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.30,0:13:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没法跟你一起骑车了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't go bike riding with you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的漂亮粉红尖头可不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, don't you worry your pretty, pink, pointy head
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.43,0:13:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以教你当个专业自行车骑手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can teach you how to be an expert bicyclist
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要当个滋冰辙起手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be an icicle mist
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lesson one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如何正确坐上自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How to properly sit on a bike
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面向前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Face forward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持双臂平行  但要松弛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,arms parallel but loose
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两脚紧紧站在沙地上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,both feet placed firmly on the sand
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay then
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.04,0:13:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Other side
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not quite
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gettin' here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是手把手来教比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we need a more hands-on approach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓牢车把
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Handlebars grasped firmly
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让屁股坐好  脚踩稳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tushy planted, feet stable
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后  哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用担心  只要掌握要领就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you just need to get the hang of it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就快掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, almost got it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nearly there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道不  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉是你对重力应付不来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you have gravity trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talkin' about
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,气球应该能让你直直稳定好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those should keep you upright
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是装辅助轮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe some training wheels
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能让你稳定点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll make you a little more stable
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我精神病医生就说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what my psychiatrist says
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得检查下你脑袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to check under the hood
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你大脑有点不太平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your brain's a bit unbalanced
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give it a try
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人应该准备好要开骑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think someone's ready to pedal
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think so, too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在轻轻踩踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, pedal nice and easy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't you let go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会把手从车上放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't take my hands off this bike
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't let go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要有东西来帮你集中注意聚焦前方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need something to help you focus
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Way ahead of ya
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.44,0:16:01.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:01.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起效了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现特别棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在认真看我做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For now, just observe me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仔细看看车要怎么骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a closer look and see how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我脚  学我做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch my feet, and do what I do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要掌握诀窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're getting it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在踏板踩快一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now pedal just a little faster
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点太快了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little too fast there, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just relax
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可放松了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm relaxed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能有专属的两人时光  阿芙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we have some time to ourselves, Puffykins
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会突然冒出来个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without any interruptions from--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个海底白痴到底在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of all that's salty
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you two dipsy doodles--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.39,0:17:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧  我有点不太会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm having a little trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教好派大星学骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,trying to teach Patrick how to ride a bicycle
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也有教不好的同学吗  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you ever had trouble teaching a student, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有些人就是教了就忘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some people are just unteachable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,650)}墙
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教了就忘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unteachable?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unteach
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次就在家约会好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're having out next date at home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道你问题出在哪吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what your problem is, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的大脑充斥着各种不重要的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your brain is just too full of unimportant knowledge
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  塞得满满当当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is pretty jam-packed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是说塞得全都是果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or is it packed with jam?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得给你脑袋腾空  方便学骑车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need to make some room in your head for bike riding
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还记得要怎么刷牙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you remember how to brush your teeth?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连怎么梳牙都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even know how to comb my teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你俩都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How to watch TV?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, not important
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.43,0:19:21.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:21.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put on your pants?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高估自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Overrated
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Family?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没多大必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unnecessary
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}消除很多记忆后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what is your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我谁是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is I?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.65,0:19:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人终于准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think someone's finally ready
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要开始骑车了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ride a bicycle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一件事得记住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's just one more thing to remember--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要开开心心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,306)}开心
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.98,0:20:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对骑车一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no knowledge of bike riding
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  现在下车还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, get off that bike before it's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1542,752)}死人山\N放弃一切希望
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可是面包人山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just Bread Man's Hill
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是面包人山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not Bread Man's Hill
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是死人山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's Dead Man's Hill
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有那么严重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is that worse?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像还挺严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sounds worse
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is worse
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I'm doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在骑车了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm bicycling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:59.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426,430)}活人平地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,332)}第一航海银行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024,386)}市政厅
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.93,0:21:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为纪念你成为有史以来最伟大的骑手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In honor of becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the greatest bicyclist who has ever lived
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.72,0:21:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要为你献上裤头村钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I present you the key to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,728)}市长
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有锁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the lock
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.52,0:21:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.77,0:21:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune you're okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.32,0:21:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是专业骑手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm an expert bicyclist now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你一路摔下了死人山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you crashed all the way down Dead Man's Hill
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都昏迷六个星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've been in a coma for six weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破我个人记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A new personal best
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉教不会你骑自行车  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I couldn't teach you how to ride a bike, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破自行车谁还用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs a dumb bike?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a bike
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hop on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.52,0:22:17.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:17.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's roll
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.69,0:22:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1076,620)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会骑派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to ride a Patrick
